resources.string: Bayar ka to farka da naurar by biyu tapping a kan da allon.

Bayar ka to gama kebul naurorin. A lokacin da kunna wasu naurar related kebul ayyuka, irin kamar yadda ADB kuma MTP, so ba zama akwai sai wannan ne naƙasasshe ko da naurar ne rebooted. ba dukan kebul naurorin so aiki.
Qara da ƙwarai na da shãfe allon haka shãfe iya zama rajista yayin da sanye safar hannu.
sa da biyu sim katin Ramin. wannan kamata ba zama kunna har akwai ne a sim katin a da biyu Ramin. (buƙatar Sake!)

Wannan ayyukansu kusa da alamurran da suka shafi tare da Snapchat, Instagram kuma wasu video rikodi apps. amfani da google AVC encoder maimakon na da HW AVC encoder. ka may bukatar to sake kunnawa da app ko sake kunnawa da naurar kafin wannan saitin daukan sakamako. wannan may har ila yau, hanyar wasu video rikodi apps ba to aiki.
